  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "chapterTitle": "礼拜五：太平洋上的灵薄狱",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300012100_3_410-745",
          "range": "410-745",
          "rangeStart": 410,
          "rangeEnd": 745,
          "markText": "弗吉尼亚号正在翻腾得越来越剧烈的涌浪中颠簸不已，舱室天花板上垂绷的一根铅丝末端上悬挂的舷灯来回摇摆，衡量出船只的侧倾角度。彼得·范·戴塞尔船长腆着肚子，俯身把塔罗牌￼摆到鲁滨孙面前。\n“先洗牌，然后翻开第一张。”他说。\n说完，他便缩进扶手椅中，叼着他的瓷烟斗，抽了一大口烟。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1713334686,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-04-17 14:18:06",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=410&rangeEnd=745",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=410&rangeEnd=745"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_6_16333-16368",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "16333-16368",
      "markText": "我希望，我苛求我周围的一切从此后都能得到衡量、证实、确认、计算、推理。",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16333&rangeEnd=16368",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16333&rangeEnd=16368"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_5_4516-4580",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4516-4580",
      "markText": "暴雨来也匆匆，去也匆匆。鲁滨孙重新找出他的衣服，也重新找到了他工作的意义与坚定的信念。他立即就克服了这一短暂但有教育意义的软弱。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4516&rangeEnd=4580",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4516&rangeEnd=4580"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_5_1622-1713",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1622-1713",
      "markText": "由于从海难那天起就忘了记日子，他对消逝的时间就只剩下一个模模糊糊的概念。在他的记忆中，日复一日，每天都那么相似，好像重叠在了一起，他甚至觉得，每一个清晨的来临，都是头一天的重新开始。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1622&rangeEnd=1713",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1622&rangeEnd=1713"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_3_6367-6404",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "6367-6404",
      "markText": "但是，塔罗牌的智慧恰恰就是如此，它从来不用明晰的语言为我们揭示我们的未来。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6367&rangeEnd=6404",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6367&rangeEnd=6404"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_12_17991-18087",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "17991-18087",
      "markText": "从此以后，他们是四个人生活在这岛上。有真鲁滨孙和竹架玩偶，有真礼拜五和沙土塑像。两个朋友有可能损害对方的一切事——咒骂、殴打、发怒——他们全都施加在对方的替身上。而两人之间，他们仍然友好相待。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=17991&rangeEnd=18087",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=17991&rangeEnd=18087"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_4_2680-2706",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2680-2706",
      "markText": "那畜生从来没见过人，是好奇令它一动不动地钉在了原地。",
      "totalCount": 78,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2680&rangeEnd=2706",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2680&rangeEnd=2706"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_14_8837-8899",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "8837-8899",
      "markText": "他们所有人追求的目的，无非就是某一种获得、某一种财富、某一种满足，但是，究竟为什么非要这一种获得、这一种财富、这一种满足呢？",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=8837&rangeEnd=8899",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=8837&rangeEnd=8899"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_6_14206-14257",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "14206-14257",
      "markText": "正在这一时刻，泰恩，这条弗吉尼亚号上的雪达犬，从灌木丛中蹿了出来，急速地跑向他，怀着一腔的友谊和柔情。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14206&rangeEnd=14257",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14206&rangeEnd=14257"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_5_3736-3782",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3736-3782",
      "markText": "一个人，只有当被一大批同类暖暖和和地簇拥着，可以毫无危险地亮出自身时，赤身裸体才是一种奢侈。",
      "totalCount": 65,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3736&rangeEnd=3782",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3736&rangeEnd=3782"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_5_4930-4971",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4930-4971",
      "markText": "鲁滨孙刚走到离它几步远的地方，它就急忙扭身后退，下嘴唇翻卷起来，发出愤怒的咆哮声。",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4930&rangeEnd=4971",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4930&rangeEnd=4971"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_7_17089-17168",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "17089-17168",
      "markText": "就这样，鲁滨孙对海岛——他的绝对孤独之女——的无上权力，一直发展到了对时间的一种支配！他有些忘乎所以地估摸，从此后，他只需把漏壶堵死，就可以制止时间的飞翔……",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=17089&rangeEnd=17168",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=17089&rangeEnd=17168"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_3_1391-1540",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1391-1540",
      "markText": "“马尔斯，”船长道，“从表面看，这个小创世神战胜了大自然。他以力量取胜，按照自己的形象强行安排了他周围一切的秩序。”",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1391&rangeEnd=1540",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1391&rangeEnd=1540"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_9_1365-1406",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1365-1406",
      "markText": "他的每一个行动，他的每一项劳作，都是向着某个人的一声召唤，但始终得不到任何的回音。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1365&rangeEnd=1406",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1365&rangeEnd=1406"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_9_6177-6209",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "6177-6209",
      "markText": "双亲一旦从不可或缺的状态中脱离出来，它们就变成了惹人讨厌的弃物。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6177&rangeEnd=6209",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6177&rangeEnd=6209"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_6_13213-13306",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "13213-13306",
      "markText": "图利的人懂得使他那图财害命、有悖社会公德的本能——荣誉感、自尊心、爱国主义、政治野心、宗教狂热、种族主义——缄默不言，而只让他那些互助合作的癖好、互惠交流的兴趣、人类团结的意义开口发言。",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13213&rangeEnd=13306",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13213&rangeEnd=13306"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_7_5421-5462",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5421-5462",
      "markText": "这时候，女巫蹲下身子，在沙滩上蜷缩成一团，又是祈祷，又是昏睡，又是呕吐，又是撒尿。",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5421&rangeEnd=5462",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5421&rangeEnd=5462"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_9_4840-5100",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "4840-5100",
      "markText": "我心中的一切：意象、梦幻、计划、幻觉、欲望、顽念。并不外在之物内在着。内在着为了外在。这整个小小的世界争先恐后地涌向大世界、真实世界的大门。而掌握着那个世界大门钥匙的是他人。",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012100&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4840&rangeEnd=5100",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9732990813ab6b3ag010f59?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4840&rangeEnd=5100"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012100_10_10426-10447",
